org.apache.poi.hssf.usermodel

Class HSSFPalette

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.poi.hssf.usermodel.HSSFPalette

  • public final class HSSFPalette
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents a workbook color palette. Internally, the XLS format refers to colors using an offset into the palette record. Thus, the first color in the palette has the index 0x8, the second has the index 0x9, etc. through 0x40(表示工作簿调色板。在内部，XLS格式指的是使用调色板记录的偏差的颜色。因此，调色板中的第一种颜色的索引为0x 8，第二种颜色的索引为0x 9，等等，直到0x 40)

      • findColor

        public HSSFColor findColor(byte red,
                           byte green,
                           byte blue)
        Finds the first occurrence of a given color(查找给定颜色的第一次出现)
        Parameters:
        red - the RGB red component, between 0 and 255 inclusive(红色--RB红色分量，介于0和255之间（含0和255）)
        green - the RGB green component, between 0 and 255 inclusive(green --RB绿色成分，介于0到255之间（含0和255）)
        blue - the RGB blue component, between 0 and 255 inclusive(蓝色--RB蓝色分量，介于0和255之间（含）)
        Returns:
        the color, or null if the color does not exist in this palette(颜色，如果此调色板中不存在颜色，则为空)

      • findSimilarColor

        public HSSFColor findSimilarColor(byte red,
                                  byte green,
                                  byte blue)
        Finds the closest matching color in the custom palette. The method for finding the distance between the colors is fairly primative.(在自定义调色板中查找最接近的匹配颜色。求颜色之间距离的方法是相当原始的。)
        Parameters:
        red - The red component of the color to match.(红色-要匹配的颜色的红色成分。)
        green - The green component of the color to match.(绿色-要匹配的颜色的绿色成分。)
        blue - The blue component of the color to match.(蓝色-要匹配的颜色的蓝色成分。)
        Returns:
        The closest color or null if there are no custom colors currently defined.(如果当前没有定义自定义颜色，则为最接近的颜色或空。)

      • addColor

        public HSSFColor addColor(byte red,
                          byte green,
                          byte blue)
        Adds a new color into an empty color slot.(将新颜色添加到空颜色槽中。)
        Parameters:
